title: Extractor Round 3: Quality Improvements
content:
## Goals
- 10 tasks across 9 extractors + cross-cutting cleanup

- YAML: remove noise names, add anchor detection (B → B+)
- Python: @property as SymbolKind::Property (B → B+)
- PHP: grouped use declarations (correctness fix)
- Razor: stop extracting assignment/element_access noise
- CSS: deduplicate @keyframes animation name
- LazyLock regex audit across 6 extractors
- Dead code cleanup across 4 extractors
